                               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nSubtraction using the *Yupana Inka Tawa Pukllay* method (<htcite0>; <htcite1>) requires prior knowledge of the movements used in addition. Therefore, we recommend studying addition through this method before proceeding (<htcite2>).",
